(6053, 997, 'project_description', 'This multi-phase, 38-story development entails the phased renovation and construction of approximately 340,000 sf. The total building will comprise a 6-story commercial base within the existing building structure, with 2 additional stories of commercial space, 4 stories of entertainment, 26 floors of a hotel rooms and base building mechanical spaces within a tower above the commercial podium.\r\n\r\nThe development will be a multi-use, integrated urban hotel, retail shopping, and entertainment-center destination. It is designed to become an immediate global attraction and a new “must-see” New York City destination by offering an unmatched shopping, hospitality, entertainment, and media experience, all within the heart of Times Square.\r\n\r\nThe project exemplifies the program and size intent of the NYC Zoning Resolution’s use, bulk and setback requirements for the Theater Sub District within the Manhattan Core. It is an ideal project in terms of size and configuration to support the City’s planning vision for this critical, image-defining area.'),
